overview: Intense, masculine passions are unleashed as two Oklahoma park service deputies, one rugged, knowing and virile, the other young, interested and ready to learn, travel miles of back country roads, where raunchy, greased-up, uninhibited superstuds await at every turn. They're all here - the masculine, blue-collar working man, the businessman, the doctor, the students, the delivery man, the county lineman and more. And they're all ready for load after load of molten, spurting man-sex. The dusty, windswept plains of Oklahoma will never be the same after these guys cross the Tulsa County Line!
title: Tulsa County Line
